headline: IDEX (IEX): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q4 Earnings?
summary: IDEX’s 24.2% return over the past six months has outpaced the S&P 500 by 17.7%, and its stock price has climbed to $206.19 per share. This performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
